getPSDELogicNodes.name: 直接SQL调用
getPSDELogicNodes.sql:
UPDATE `INTERNAL_MESSAGE` t1 SET t1.`STATUS` = 'READ' 
WHERE 
( ( t1.`STATUS` = 'RECEIVED' )  AND  t1.`RECEIVER` = ? 
 AND  t1.`SYSTEM_TAG` = ? )
